			<h4>NC Department of Transportation Fines</h4>
			<p>There are applicable fines assessed by the DOT on drivers who have been convicted of "driving while impaired".  Those fines are separate from court cost, attorney fees and other costs. For updated information regarding such fines see <a target="_blank" href="http://www.ncga.state.nc.us">www.ncga.state.nc.us</a></p>
